{
  "bio": [
    "Kishore Jain owns and runs Chennai-based Khazana Jewellery, which sells gold and diamond jewellery.",
    "Khazana, which means treasure in Sanskrit, has more than 50 stores across India and two stores in Sharjah.",
    "Jain took over the wholesale jewelry business founded by his late father, Bhoormal Sehsmalji, and set up his first retail store in Nellore, a city in the southern state of Andhra Pradesh in 1976.",
    "He shifted base to Chennai city in 1989."
  ],
  "about": [
    "His father founded the business as Jewellery House in Nellore in 1954.",
    "His ancestors hail from a village in Rajasthan."
  ]
}